<scriptment id="45000" point="conceptualization_2" localizationstatus="original" fictionaldate="2011-08-09" status="final">
	<part>
		<narration>Yuki and the team sit around the Chabudai, the foundation of all game development.</narration>
		<line id="1000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Second time's the charm, right?</line>
		<narration>While making decisions for the concept for the next game, the team banters on.</narration>
		<condition>
		
		
			<choice number="1">
				<comment>The player chooses Nintendo DS as a platform.</comment>
				<narration>Everyone slams on the table.</narration>
				<line id="1000" speaker="ganpu" voicelang="ja">Nintendo DS? After that last demonstration?</line>
				<line id="2000" speaker="dan" voicelang="ja">After Dreamcast's murder, we developed for Sony.</line>
				<line id="3000" speaker="dan" voicelang="ja">Such is the life of a third-party, dancing for the swine.</line>
				<line id="4000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">There are 200 million American DS owners.</line>
				<line id="5000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">They've got us by the balls.</line>
			</choice>
			<choice number="2">
				<comment>The player chooses Sony PSP.</comment>
				<narration>Shimizu frowns.</narration>
				<line id="6000" speaker="hanako" voicelang="ja">PSP? What of the pirates?</line>
				<line id="7000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">A play is a play.</line>
			</choice>
			<choice number="3">
				<comment>The player chooses Macintosh.</comment>
				<line id="8000" speaker="takuya" voicelang="ja">Mac users play games?</line>
				<narration>Yuki looks around. <comment>She then looks at the camera.</comment></narration>
				<condition>
				
					<choice number="1">
						<comment>This is the Mac OS build.</comment>
						<line id="9000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Maybe!</line>
						<narration>Yuki winks.</narration>
					</choice>
					<choice number="2">
						<comment>This is not the Mac OS build.</comment>
						<line id="10000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Nah.</line>
					</choice>
				</condition>
			</choice>
		</condition>
		
		<narration>Yuki claps.</narration>
		<line id="11000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Mobilize!</line>
	</part>
</scriptment>